text: Jurášek is a 1957 Czechoslovak drama film, directed by Miroslav Cikán. It stars Karel Hašler jr., Vladimir Gulyaev, and Karel Höger. ==References== Category:1957 films Category:Czechoslovak films Category:Czechoslovak drama films Category:1957 drama films Category:Films directed by Miroslav Cikán Category:Czech war films Category:Czech children's films Category:Czech resistance to Nazi occupation in film
